textBox.richText: Luckily for her, we all got to celebrate Mariann’s 30th birthday in New York City. Andrew thoughtfully planned out a number of ‘30 centric’ activities including a trip to the Thirty Thirty hotel, 30 Street Guitars and 30 Rockefeller Centre. At either end of all this touring was obviously food with breakfast at the W Hotel and an amazing lunch at Nougatine in Central Park. As seems to be the norm, New York put on a great day - perfect for Mariann on her birthday and even better for our pics atop Rockefeller Centre
